{"title":"Fara F/GR gravel road bike takes QR integrated bikepacking tech off tarmac","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/11/04/fara-f-gr-gravel-road-bike-takes-qr-integrated-bikepacking-tech-off-tarmac/","date":1636056817000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160510/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_side.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160510/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_side-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, riding\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160510/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_side-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160510/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_side-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160510/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_side-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160510/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_side-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160510/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_side-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160510/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_side-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-277477\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>The new carbon Fara F/GR gravel bike is the almost obvious extension of the Norwegian bike company’s adventure bikepacking line-up. Their third bike to feature magnetic quick-release, integrated bikepacking bags, the new F/GR gravel road bike is meant to open up any remaining hard surface track for exploration with 50mm tire clearance and quick all-terrain handling.</p><h2>Fara F/GR carbon adventure gravel road bike</h2><div id=\"attachment_277533\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160505/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277533\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160505/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_complete.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, complete\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160505/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_complete.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160505/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_complete-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160505/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_complete-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160505/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_complete-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160505/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_complete-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160505/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_complete-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277533\">c. Fara Cycling</p></div><p>First, there was the Fara Cycling <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/01/28/fara-f-ar-integrates-all-road-gravel-bike-with-quick-release-strapless-bikepacking-bags/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">F/AR all-road</a> bike that was kind of ‘gravel light’ with room for 35mm knobby tires. Then, their next bike surprisingly went smaller, channeling the road riding background of founder and ex-pro Jeff Webb. That aero endurance <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/01/fara-f-rd-aero-road-bike-adapts-integrated-all-road-bikepacking-tech-to-smooth-roads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">F/RD road</a> bike dialed it back slightly to 32mm to focus more on riding fast, but was still kinda ‘all-road’.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160501/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_off-road.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160501/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_off-road.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, riding\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160501/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_off-road.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160501/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_off-road-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160501/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_off-road-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160501/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_off-road-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160501/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_off-road-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160501/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_off-road-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>Now, the new F/GR gravel bike does pretty much exactly the same thing, but bigger.</p><h3>Adventure capability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160455/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_pair.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160455/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_pair.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, #baaw\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160455/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_pair.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160455/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_pair-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160455/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_pair-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160455/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_pair-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160455/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_pair-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160455/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_pair-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>With clearance for a full 700 x 50mm gravel tire, this is the dropbar bikepacking adventure bike many were hoping for after getting teased by the first integrated all-road bike almost a year ago. You don’t actually need to go that big to get the most out of this new bike. Fara says their sweet spot is actually around a 43mm tire for the best blend of speed and mixed-surface versatility.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160451/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Fidloc-Roswheel-bags.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160451/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Fidloc-Roswheel-bags.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, Fidloc Roswheel IBS bags\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160451/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Fidloc-Roswheel-bags.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160451/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Fidloc-Roswheel-bags-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160451/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Fidloc-Roswheel-bags-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160451/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Fidloc-Roswheel-bags-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160451/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Fidloc-Roswheel-bags-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>Fara’s bikes are all about going further and include IBS (Integrated Bikepacking System) direct mounts inside the main triangle for magnetic <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=fidlock\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fidloc</a> posts that let you quickly install or remove the F/GR’s integrated &nbsp;<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=roswheel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Roswheel</a> bikepacking frame bag without the need for straps. The frameset also includes a set of toptube bosses for a direct mount bento bag, bosses under the downtube, and 3-pack anything cage mounts on each fork leg.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160447/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_In-Frame-Stash-Hatch.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160447/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_In-Frame-Stash-Hatch.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, In-Frame Stash Hatch\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160447/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_In-Frame-Stash-Hatch.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160447/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_In-Frame-Stash-Hatch-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160447/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_In-Frame-Stash-Hatch-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160447/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_In-Frame-Stash-Hatch-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160447/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_In-Frame-Stash-Hatch-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>New for the F/GR, the regular set of bottle bosses on the downtube also conceal a new In-Frame Stash Hatch, a small port that opens up to allow you to store small spares and a tool for example low inside the frame.</p><h3>Mixed-surface gravel geometry</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04150829/Fara-F-GR-carbon-adventure-gravel-road-bike_geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04150829/Fara-F-GR-carbon-adventure-gravel-road-bike_geometry.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon adventure gravel road bike, geometry\" width=\"1490\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04150829/Fara-F-GR-carbon-adventure-gravel-road-bike_geometry.jpg 1490w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04150829/Fara-F-GR-carbon-adventure-gravel-road-bike_geometry-297x153.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04150829/Fara-F-GR-carbon-adventure-gravel-road-bike_geometry-800x412.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04150829/Fara-F-GR-carbon-adventure-gravel-road-bike_geometry-120x62.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04150829/Fara-F-GR-carbon-adventure-gravel-road-bike_geometry-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1490px) 100vw, 1490px\"></a></p><p>Now 1° slacker than the all-road bike, 2° slacker than the road version, the new gravel bike gets a longer wheelbase, longer chainstays, and longer front center &amp; frame reach to add more stability over rougher terrain and with heavier loads.</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160443/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_red-frameset.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160443/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_red-frameset.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, frameset\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160443/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_red-frameset.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160443/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_red-frameset-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160443/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_red-frameset-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160443/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_red-frameset-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160443/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_red-frameset-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160443/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_red-frameset-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p>Like the other two Fara Cycling bikes, the F/GR is a made-in-Taiwan carbon frameset built for adventure riding. That means versatility, comfort, and accessory mounting takes precedence over absolute lightweight – yet it still comes in at a competitive 1050g claimed weight (53cm).</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160439/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_angled-rear.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160439/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_angled-rear.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, angled rear\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160439/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_angled-rear.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160439/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_angled-rear-297x186.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160439/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_angled-rear-800x500.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160439/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_angled-rear-120x75.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160439/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_angled-rear-768x480.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160439/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_angled-rear-1536x960.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>To deliver big on comfort, the F/GR features curved seatstays for extra give, dropped &amp; combined with a subtle rear wheel cutout to allow the seattube to flex as well.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160436/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_BB-front-derailleur-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160436/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_BB-front-derailleur-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, T47 BB\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160436/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_BB-front-derailleur-detail.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160436/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_BB-front-derailleur-detail-297x165.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160436/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_BB-front-derailleur-detail-800x444.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160436/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_BB-front-derailleur-detail-120x67.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160436/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_BB-front-derailleur-detail-768x427.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160436/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_BB-front-derailleur-detail-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p>Like the other bikes, it features fully internal cable touring through the Token S-Box headset system, 12mm thru-axles, flat mount disc brakes (direct, no adapter 160mm front brake mount), 1x or 2x compatibility, a universal derailleur hanger (UDH), a threaded T47 bottom bracket, hidden full-coverage fender mounts, plus a round 27.2mm seatpost with a conventional external clamp.</p><h3>Fara F/GR all-road gravel bike – Pricing &amp; current availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160432/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_NDS-sunset.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160432/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_NDS-sunset.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, sunset\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160432/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_NDS-sunset.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160432/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_NDS-sunset-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160432/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_NDS-sunset-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160432/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_NDS-sunset-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160432/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_NDS-sunset-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160432/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_NDS-sunset-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p>Being sold direct-to-consumer globally, Fara says they’ll ship their new F/GR gravel bike starting in April 2022.</p><div id=\"attachment_277524\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160428/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Signature-Series-frameset.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277524\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160428/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Signature-Series-frameset.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, frameset\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1100\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160428/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Signature-Series-frameset.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160428/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Signature-Series-frameset-297x163.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160428/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Signature-Series-frameset-800x440.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160428/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Signature-Series-frameset-120x66.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160428/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Signature-Series-frameset-768x422.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160428/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Signature-Series-frameset-1536x845.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277524\">2022 Fara F-GR Signature frameset</p></div><p>The new bikes are being sold in four sizes (S 49cm, M 53cm, L 56cm &amp; L 59cm) in Fara’s four standard colors – Fjord Green, Winter Sky Blue, Wet Asphalt &amp; Morell Red. A special Signature series frameset is also available in limited numbers during this pre-order phase only, in metallic Phyllite silver/gray with Rust graphics.</p><div id=\"attachment_277523\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160423/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Shimano-GRX-complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277523\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160423/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Shimano-GRX-complete.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, Shimano GRX\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160423/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Shimano-GRX-complete.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160423/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Shimano-GRX-complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160423/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Shimano-GRX-complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160423/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Shimano-GRX-complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160423/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Shimano-GRX-complete-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160423/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Shimano-GRX-complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277523\">2022 Fara F-GR GRX 1×11</p></div><p>For now, fully refundable 1000€ pre-orders are being offered with framesets ultimately selling for 2500€ or complete bikes starting from 3300€ built up with Shimano GRX 810 1×11 (including free fenders for pre-orders).</p><div id=\"attachment_277522\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160410/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Campagnolo-Ekar-complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277522\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160410/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Campagnolo-Ekar-complete.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, Campy Ekar\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160410/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Campagnolo-Ekar-complete.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160410/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Campagnolo-Ekar-complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160410/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Campagnolo-Ekar-complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160410/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Campagnolo-Ekar-complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160410/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Campagnolo-Ekar-complete-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160410/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_Campagnolo-Ekar-complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277522\">2022 Fara F-GR Ekar 1×13</p></div><p>Each buyer can use Fara’s online customizer to customize their build, with drivetrain options available from Shimano Campagnolo (add 600€ for Ekar or 800€ for Di2) plus plenty of other options to make your gravel bike unique.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Fara F-GR carbon bikepacking adventure gravel road bike, group ride\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-120x67.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/04160403/Fara-F-GR-carbon-bikepacking-adventure-gravel-road-bike_group-ride-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://launch.faracycling.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>FaraCycling.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"7c8e9ed227d80bcf97517d962bfe4a2cfa94f4820d5d45b6ad465b7ed5e098c7","category":"Cycling"}